<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>رَوَى عنهُ العَلاءُ بنُ عَبدِ الكَريمِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٥٩٦]</span> أَبُو الكِباشِ <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رَوى عنهُ كِدامُ بنُ عَبدِ الرَّحمنِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٥٩٧]</span> أَبُو كامِلٍ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>سمِعَ زُهيرَ بنَ مُعاوِيةَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>رَوى عنهُ أَحمدُ بنُ حَنبلٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
